ince obtaining his first set of turntables at just 13, Brighton based electronic DJ & producer Dismantle has since risen to the forefront of the underground dance world, bringing raw beats, pounding basslines & new, undiscovered sounds to the UK Bass scene. Fusing the raucous energy of Drum & Bass and Grime with the smoother rhythmic thrust of House, Dismantle's unique sound has gained him regular support from Radio 1 DJ's Diplo, Annie Mac, Skrillex, Mista Jam & Skream & with his monthly show on Rinse FM his fan base is rapidly rising across the globe. Now a key member of Shy FX's Digital Soundboy crew, Dismantle has provided remixes for Sub Focus, A-Trak, Jakwob, Toddla T & Zinc and collaborated on tracks with bass legends Caspa, Breakage & DJ Die.
